# 📸 Real-Time Responsive Image Gallery

This project is a modern, responsive, and dynamic **image gallery** built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. 
It fetches **real-time images** from the **Unsplash API** based on categories like **nature, travel, people, animals, and technology**. 
It features a **lightbox view**, **smooth transitions**, **image navigation**, and displays **photo credits** per Unsplash guidelines.



## 🌟 Features

- 🔍 Real-time image loading using the Unsplash API
- 🧭 Category-based image filters (Nature, Travel, Animals, People, Tech)
- 💡 Lightbox view with next/previous navigation
- ✨ Hover effects and smooth zoom transitions
- 📷 Automatically displays **photographer credit** and photo link
- 📱 Fully **responsive** layout using CSS Grid and Flexbox
- 🌙 Beautiful UI with modern design and animations

---

## 🔧 Tech Stack

- **HTML5**
- **CSS3** (Flexbox + Grid + Transitions)
- **JavaScript (ES6)**
- **Unsplash Developer API**


